I was using KIS, KAS, MechJeb and Kerbal Engineer Redux and everything was alright. But I decided to install Infernal Robotics, Kerbal Alarm Clock, SCANsat, StageRecovery and Contracts Windows +.After I installed I noticed that the icons of Infernal Robotics and from Alarm Clock was working but from SCANsat, StageRecovery and Contracts Windows + was not (images below). Someone knows what to do?

I already tryed Contract +, StageRecovery and SCANsat alone and the icons didn't worked anyway.

I'm using KSP 1.0.4 on a Windows 64 bits, in a version before I used the sames mods in the same computer and it worked (I think it was 1.0.2) and so I tried it in that version and didn't work again.
